<http://example.org/req/728#Req_0> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Thing,
        ns1:InformationContentEntity,
        ns1:RequirementSpecification ;
    rdfs:comment "EV.7.4.5: The voltage rating of the Overcurrent Protection must be equal to or higher than the maximum segment voltage. Overcurrent Protection is not required on a voltage sense wire if all three of the following conditions are met: AMS is a distributed AMS system (one cell measurement per board); Sense wire length is less than 25 mm; AMS board has Overcurrent Protection. (EV.7.5 Accumulator Temperature EV.7.5.1 context omitted).",
        "EV.7.4.5: The voltage rating of the Overcurrent Protection must be equal to or higher than the maximum segment voltage. Overcurrent Protection is not required on a voltage sense wire if all three of the following conditions are met: AMS is a distributed AMS system (one cell measurement per board); Sense wire length is less than 25 mm; AMS board has Overcurrent Protection. (EV.7.5 Accumulator Temperature EV.7.5.1 context omitted)."@en ;
